Detailed Description

An error reply for a prevoiusly sent asynchronous request.

Parameters:
requestID The RequestID for the request function call.
statusCode The StatusCode for request.
statusMessage The string message for the status.
statusURL An URL to open for the status.
statusData Status data for the status. May be empty. Used to indicate an appropriate client side action in order to handle an error. For instance it can be used to indicate which product id that could be purchased for expired rights. See BillingInterface for further documentation.
